ghost.objects

Class GameMap

  • java.lang.Object
    • ghost.objects.GameMap

  • public class GameMap
extends java.lang.Object
    Reads the config.json file, and manages all the static objects related to the game. Also handles the modes for the ghosts.

    • Constructor Detail

      • GameMap

        public GameMap()
        GameMap constructor. Read the config.json file, and get the file name, player lives, movement speed, and the mode lengths. Also stores the starting position of the player and the ghosts, and set the gameMapMatrix.
